body.name: Vinsetto High Back Home Office Chair, Fabric Computer Desk Chair with Adjustable Headrest, Lumbar Support, Armrest, Foot Rest, Reclining Back, Black
features: Long Lasting Comfort: You're going to need a home office chair that can hold up to those long work days and still keep your back supported and comfortable, this chair has got you covered. The thick padding will ease muscle pain associated from sitting for long periods of time. A linen-feel fabric back allows air to circulate while you work, helping to keep you cooler throughout long workdays.

Lean Back and Relax: When you're ready for a break, stretch back in this swivel chair with 100°/115°/130° reclining, to take the pressure off your lower lumbar and spine while working, reading or studying. Kick your feet out onto the footrest for the ultimate feeling of comfort and just push it back in when you're ready to get back to work. Ease neck and lumbar pressure and tension with a headrest pillow and lumbar support.

Adjust Your Position: This comfy desk chair is height-adjustable, so you can match your desk and sitting preferences. The headrest can move up or down, rotate, removable to fit how you rest your neck while sitting and helps prevent shoulder pain.
Back Support: This comfortable office chair has a high back, so you have head, neck, middle and lower lumbar support that keeps you comfortable for hours.
Chair for Desk Information: Overall Dimensions: 26" W x 22.75" D x 43.25" -46.5" H, Seat Size: 19.75" W x 19.75" D, Seat Height: 17.25" -20.5". Weight Capacity: 265 lbs. Assembly required.
body.description: If you work from home or spend a lot of time in your office, you need a chair that's going to hold up if you're studying for a big final, or finishing on a big work project. This computer chair from Vinsetto can not only keep up, but goes above and beyond with it's relaxing thick padding and recline. Comfort and functionality are important for a home office desk chair and Vinsetto knows how to deliver. Take a break and stretch out with 100°/115°/130° reclining angle Adjustable seat height to fit your sitting style Lumbar support relieves your low back pressure The headrest can move up or down, rotate, removable Retractable footrest so you can prop your feet up while you lay back The linen-feel fabric is breathable and soft Swivel wheels and seat ensure easy and quick mobility Assembly required
